back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zye1719506814289.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zye1719506814289.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zye1719506814289.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zay1665702690036\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                    \n operation init\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zay1665702690036__operation_init_400946\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Defines the component behavior when a component instance is created with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> (or by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> when <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> is executed implicitly).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zay1665702690036__topic_d118595e1_d118596e1_d118597e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104zye1719506814289_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"zay1665702690036__codeblock_zgn_s2l_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">   operation init\n      {<var class=\"keyword varname\">variablesBlock</var>}\n      Your code here ...\n   end</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zay1665702690036__topic_d84602e1_d84603e1_d84604e1_d84605e1_d84606e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d346621e75\">\n                     \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zay1665702690036__d6385e20\">All components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zay1665702690036__topic_d84607e1_d84608e1_d84609e1_d84610e1_d84611e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d346621e84\">\n                     \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zay1665702690036__p_d118607e1_d118608e1_d118609e1\">If an Init operation has been defined in the component, it is executed before the new instance is created. Since the new instance does not really exist at this point, the Init operation should not perform any action that involves the new instance. For example, it should not use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">deleteinstance</span> on the instance or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> for an operation contained in the instance.</p>\n<div class=\"div\"> </div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qom1665703129290.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Script Container</a><p>Location for defining the ProcScript modules of the associated object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tcd1719504517290.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>operation cleanup</a><p>Defines the component behavior when a component instance is removed.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vrb1707739762002.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Operations</a><p>Operations are ProcScript modules that are analogous to methods in other programming languages; they perform specific actions and can be activated by other ProcScript modules, and even by non-Uniface components.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7425270\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7425270\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "operation init Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 operation init Defines the component behavior when a component instance is created with newinstance (or by activate when newinstance is executed implicitly). Explain this code operation init { variablesBlock } Your code here ... end Copy Use All components. Description If an Init operation has been defined in the component, it is executed before the new instance is created. Since the new instance does not really exist at this point, the Init operation should not perform any action that involves the new instance. For example, it should not use deleteinstance on the instance or activate for an operation contained in the instance. Related Links Script Container Location for defining the ProcScript modules of the associated object. operation cleanup Defines the component behavior when a component instance is removed. Operations Operations are ProcScript modules that are analogous to methods in other programming languages; they perform specific actions and can be activated by other ProcScript modules, and even by non-Uniface components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}